H0_1.g_brief: Opens calculator mode menu (Standard, Scientific, Programmer, etc.)

H2_1.g_brief: Memory Clear - clears all stored memory values

H3_1.g_brief: Memory Recall - recalls the value stored in memory

H4_1.g_brief: Toggle sign - changes positive to negative or vice versa

H5_1.g_brief: Reciprocal - calculates 1 divided by the current number

H6_1.g_brief: Percentage - calculates percentage of a number

H10_1.g_brief: Memory Add - adds current number to memory

H11_1.g_brief: Memory Subtract - subtracts current number from memory

H12_1.g_brief: Memory Store - stores current number in memory

H13_1.g_brief: Clear Entry - clears the last entered number

H14_1.g_brief: Square - calculates the square of the current number

H19_1.g_brief: Square Root - calculates the square root of the current number

H21_1.g_brief: Clear - clears all calculations and resets calculator

H25_1.g_brief: Backspace - deletes the last entered digit

H28_1.g_brief: Equals - calculates and displays the result

H29_1.g_brief: Calculator display showing current number or result

H31_1.g_brief: Text message indicating no history available

H32_1.g_brief: Opens memory panel to view stored values

H33_2.g_brief: Maximizes or restores the calculator window

HL0_1.g_brief: Opens the main menu with application options
